99
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,210
I’ll make a quick call.

100
00:06:58,060 --> 00:06:58,730
Zhong Zhen...

101
00:06:58,850 --> 00:06:59,970
Where is he?

102
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:01,700
Dr. Qin, I...

103
00:07:01,700 --> 00:07:02,500
He isn’t here.

104
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:03,210
Follow me.

105
00:07:05,910 --> 00:07:07,240
Is it serious?

106
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,090
You should be prepared.

107
00:07:12,650 --> 00:07:13,450
Go in.

108
00:07:19,770 --> 00:07:20,480
Is he asleep?

109
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:21,570
He just drifted off.

110
00:07:23,420 --> 00:07:24,970
How did he develop complications?

111
00:07:25,700 --> 00:07:27,250
He had a fever a few days ago

112
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:28,570
which had weakened his immune system.

113
00:07:29,450 --> 00:07:30,570
After you two fought,

114
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:32,450
