115
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:34,040
but worked all day,

116
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:36,210
and took up all emergency surgeries.

117
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:39,380
Hey... Hey... Rong.

118
00:07:39,770 --> 00:07:40,330
What are you doing?

119
00:07:40,330 --> 00:07:41,240
Don’t cry.

120
00:07:45,260 --> 00:07:46,410
Don’t be sad.

121
00:07:47,570 --> 00:07:48,300
Look at me.

122
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,090
I’m fine.

123
00:07:49,090 --> 00:07:49,860
All good.

124
00:07:49,860 --> 00:07:50,420
I’m not dying.

125
00:07:50,420 --> 00:07:51,120
Zhong Zhen,

126
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:52,530
