between me and Mr. Shangguan.

134
00:08:12,570 --> 00:08:13,330
I know.

135
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:15,530
Do you know how worried I was?

136
00:08:15,650 --> 00:08:17,670
Even Dr. Qin lied for you, too.

137
00:08:17,740 --> 00:08:18,530
Please don’t be mad.

138
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:20,090
I’m sorry.

139
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:22,650
But you didn’t answer my calls

140
00:08:22,650 --> 00:08:23,450
or messages.

141
00:08:23,450 --> 00:08:25,040
I wasn’t sure if I could see you

142
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:26,700
or if you’d come.

143
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:27,450
So...

144
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:29,970
Hey,

145
00:08:30,090 --> 00:08:31,120
I know I made a mistake,

146
00:08:32,090 --> 00:08:33,330
but I couldn’t wait to see you.

147
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:35,680
Don’t do this ever again.

148
00:08:38,370 --> 00:08:41,050
So are there complications or not?

149
00:08:41,050 --> 00:08:41,810
