174
00:10:19,970 --> 00:10:20,570
Look.

175
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:50,370
Hurry!

176
00:10:50,370 --> 00:10:51,050
I’m waiting for you.

177
00:10:52,940 --> 00:10:53,600
Let’s go.

178
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:02,020
