179
00:11:02,020 --> 00:11:03,450
You can say it now.

180
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:05,560
I love you.

181
00:11:05,650 --> 00:11:06,290
What?

182
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:08,660
Say that again.

183
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:11,970
One more time.

184
00:11:11,970 --> 00:11:13,130
I didn’t get it.

185
00:11:13,130 --> 00:11:13,610
No.

186
00:11:13,610 --> 00:11:14,730
I’ve said it already.

187
00:11:15,610 --> 00:11:16,370
Wait for me.

188
00:11:16,700 --> 00:11:18,040
Say it again.

189
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:36,880
Aren’t we supposed to
have breakfast together?

190
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:38,090
Where is he?

191
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:06,810
Why are you half-naked?

192
00:12:09,330 --> 00:12:10,570
Why would I shower

193
00:12:10,570 --> 00:12:12,890
