194
00:12:12,890 --> 00:12:14,400
You’re a lawyer.

195
00:12:14,850 --> 00:12:16,240
Should I sue you for trespassing?

196
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:20,000
Cover yourself first.

197
00:12:20,210 --> 00:12:21,410
I’ll come later.

198
00:12:21,410 --> 00:12:22,050
Hold on.

199
00:12:23,610 --> 00:12:24,720
Pass me that jacket.

200
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:35,850
I said to pass me that jacket,

201
00:12:35,850 --> 00:12:36,880
