226
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:38,880
Oh.

227
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:40,670
That’s it?

228
00:13:40,950 --> 00:13:42,270
I won’t let it slide

229
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:44,030
next time.

230
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:48,030
My security password is your birthday.

231
00:13:48,730 --> 00:13:50,570
But text me before you come.

232
00:13:50,700 --> 00:13:51,700
I’m not open to unannounced visits

233
00:13:51,700 --> 00:13:52,640
as you are.

234
00:14:07,540 --> 00:14:08,360
Sorry,

235
00:14:08,970 --> 00:14:11,170
did I disturb you?

236
00:14:11,730 --> 00:14:14,170
I... I... I guess

237
00:14:14,450 --> 00:14:16,240
I hit the frame by accident.

238
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:19,000
I’m only half awake.

239
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:20,930
You’re up early.

240
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,450
Didn’t you sleep well last night?

241
00:14:22,450 --> 00:14:23,370
You could’ve slept in.

242
00:14:23,370 --> 00:14:24,330
I’m fine.

243
00:14:25,020 --> 00:14:26,640
The hotel still needs me.

244
00:14:27,090 --> 00:14:31,480
I’m healthy enough to go to work.

245
00:14:31,850 --> 00:14:33,000
Don’t worry about me.

246
00:14:34,450 --> 00:14:35,850
I’m taking the breakfast to go.

247
00:14:36,370 --> 00:14:37,050
See you.

248
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:41,450
Call me if you need anything.

249
00:14:47,780 --> 00:14:48,880
She must’ve

250
00:14:49,450 --> 00:14:50,880
been sad all night.

251
00:14:51,330 --> 00:14:52,730
When her previous relationships failed,

252
00:14:52,730 --> 00:14:54,450
she’d cry and make a fuss

253
00:14:54,570 --> 00:14:56,000
but soon get over them.

254
00:14:56,420 --> 00:14:57,450
This time,

255
00:14:57,850 --> 00:15:00,050
she’s forcing herself to look happy.

256
00:15:00,330 --> 00:15:02,810
Apparently, she can’t get over Wen Rang.

257
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:06,970
If he has no feelings for her,

258
00:15:06,970 --> 00:15:09,170
could he keep a distance from her?

259
00:15:09,170 --> 00:15:09,970
OK.

260
00:15:10,300 --> 00:15:11,640
I’ll talk to him.

261
00:15:20,100 --> 00:15:23,700
<i>One Palace Home</i>

262
00:15:34,300 --> 00:15:36,020
Pull yourself together

263
00:15:36,020 --> 00:15:37,520
or Cong Rong will be worried.

264
00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:47,940
