265
00:15:47,940 --> 00:15:48,720
Guys,

266
00:15:49,700 --> 00:15:51,330
those four patients came in last night.

267
00:15:51,330 --> 00:15:53,760
Their conditions are critical.

268
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:55,670
There’s a long day

269
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:56,980
ahead of us.

270
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:59,190
Are you clear about everything?

271
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:01,580
Treat them according to our discussion.

272
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:02,500
