273
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:04,980
Chen,

274
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:06,700
go get some rest.

275
00:16:06,830 --> 00:16:07,820
You look pale.

276
00:16:07,950 --> 00:16:08,740
Thank you, Director.

277
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:14,820
I’ve almost reached my limit.

278
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,100
One more shift,

279
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,640
I’d end up in ER.

280
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:18,700
You must’ve been cursed

281
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:21,670
with night shifts.

282
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:24,860
You’re such a jinx!

283
00:16:31,590 --> 00:16:32,980
That look of yours

284
00:16:34,310 --> 00:16:35,510
is never good.

285
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:36,910
You’re wise, Boss.

286
00:16:37,950 --> 00:16:39,390
It’s the patient in Bed 3.

